                "link": "https://stackoverflow.com/users/1636828/beej",
                "reputation": 38,
                "display_name": "beej"
            },
            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 3.0",
            "score": 0,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1432225897,
            "creation_date": 1432225897,
            "body": "<p>If you must use a BufferedReader, you can use the <code>int read()<\/code> method instead of <code>String readLine()<\/code>. See the BufferedReader <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/io/BufferedReader.html#read()\" rel=\"nofollow\">javadocs<\/a><\/p>\n",
